"629","<TEXT>"
"630","Exhibit 77E"
"631","LEGAL PROCEEDINGS"
"632","Since February 2004, Federated and related"
"633","entities (collectively, Federated) have"
"634","been named as defendants in several lawsuits,"
"635","that were consolidated into a single"
"636","action in the United States District Court for"
"637","the Western District of Pennsylvania,"
"638","alleging excessive advisory fees involving one"
